  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-commodity\">temporary frigate upgrade</span> that lasts for one expedition.<br><br>This powerful analytic computer overclocks the existing fleet systems, allowing for faster-than-light calculations. Heat is a problem, and the chips do not last long.",
